001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.calculator;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import java.util.Arrays;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.models.InsulinUnit;
006import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.shared.L;
007
008import org.apache.commons.lang3.tuple.Pair;
009
010import java.util.ArrayList;
011import java.util.Arrays;
012import java.util.HashSet;
013import java.util.LinkedHashSet;
014import java.util.List;
015import java.util.Set;
016import java.util.TreeSet;
017import java.util.stream.Collectors;
018
019/**
020 * Contains logic for deciding an estimated bolus amount given inputs and current pump/CGM status.
021 */
022public class BolusCalculator {
023    private static final String TAG = "BolusCalculator";
024
025    // input fields
026    private final BolusParameters userInputParameters;
027    private final BolusCalcDataSnapshot dataSnapshot;
028    private final BolusCalcLastBG lastBG;
029
030    BolusCalculator(BolusParameters userInputParameters, BolusCalcDataSnapshot dataSnapshot, BolusCalcLastBG lastBG) {
031        this.userInputParameters = userInputParameters;
032        this.dataSnapshot = dataSnapshot;
033        this.lastBG = lastBG;
034    }
035
036    /**
037     * @return the {@link BolusCalcComponent} representing insulin for carbs
038     */
039    public BolusCalcComponent getAddedFromCarbs() {
040        double addedFromCarbs = 0;
041        List<BolusCalcCondition> conditions = new ArrayList<>();
042
043        if (dataSnapshot == null) {
044            return zeroWithCondition(new BolusCalcCondition.WaitingOnPrecondition("carb ratio from data snapshot"));
045        }
046
047        if (userInputParameters.carbsGrams == null) {
048            return zeroWithCondition(new BolusCalcCondition.NonActionDecision("not adding units for carbs", "no carbs provided"));
049        }
050
051        double ratio = InsulinUnit.from1000To1(dataSnapshot.carbRatio);
052        if (ratio > 0) {
053            addedFromCarbs = userInputParameters.carbsGrams / ratio;
054        } else {
055            conditions.add(new BolusCalcCondition.FailedSanityCheck("raw carb ratio is invalid: " + dataSnapshot.carbRatio));
056        }
057
058        return new BolusCalcComponent(BolusCalcUnits.doublePrecision(addedFromCarbs), conditions);
059    }
060
061    /**
062     * @return the {@link BolusCalcComponent} representing insulin for the current BG correction
063     */
064    public BolusCalcComponent getAddedFromGlucose() {
065        double addedFromBG = 0;
066
067        if (dataSnapshot == null) {
068            return zeroWithCondition(new BolusCalcCondition.WaitingOnPrecondition("data snapshot"));
069        }
070
071        if (lastBG == null) {
072            return zeroWithCondition(new BolusCalcCondition.WaitingOnPrecondition("last BG"));
073        }
074
075        Integer lastBGValue = null;
076        List<BolusCalcCondition> conditions = new ArrayList<>();
077        if (userInputParameters.glucoseMgdl != null) {
078            lastBGValue = userInputParameters.glucoseMgdl;
079            conditions.add(new BolusCalcCondition.DataDecision("using BG user input"));
080        } else {
081            Pair<Integer, List<BolusCalcCondition>> lastBG = this.lastBG.determineLastBG();
082            conditions = new ArrayList<>(lastBG.getRight());
083
084            if (lastBG.getLeft() == null) {
085                conditions.add(new BolusCalcCondition.NonActionDecision("not adding units for BG", "no BG provided"));
086                return new BolusCalcComponent(0.0, conditions);
087            }
088            lastBGValue = lastBG.getLeft();
089        }
090
091        if (dataSnapshot.targetBg < 40 || dataSnapshot.targetBg > 400) {
092            conditions.add(new BolusCalcCondition.FailedSanityCheck("target BG is out of range or empty in pump profile"));
093            return new BolusCalcComponent(0.0, conditions);
094        }
095
096        if (dataSnapshot.isf <= 0) {
097            conditions.add(new BolusCalcCondition.FailedSanityCheck("no Insulin Sensitivity Factor present in pump profile"));
098            return new BolusCalcComponent(0.0, conditions);
099        }
100
101        int bgDiff = lastBGValue - dataSnapshot.targetBg;
102        addedFromBG = (1.0 * bgDiff) / dataSnapshot.isf;
103
104        return new BolusCalcComponent(BolusCalcUnits.doublePrecision(addedFromBG), conditions);
105    }
106
107    /**
108     * @return the {@link BolusCalcComponent} representing insulin for the current IOB correction
109     */
110    public BolusCalcComponent getAddedFromIOB() {
111        double addedFromIOB = 0;
112        List<BolusCalcCondition> conditions = new ArrayList<>();
113
114        if (dataSnapshot == null) {
115            return zeroWithCondition(new BolusCalcCondition.WaitingOnPrecondition("data snapshot"));
116        }
117
118        if (dataSnapshot.iob > 0) {
119            addedFromIOB = -1 * dataSnapshot.iob;
120        }
121
122        return new BolusCalcComponent(BolusCalcUnits.doublePrecision(addedFromIOB), conditions);
123    }
124
125    /**
126     * @return a {@link BolusCalcDecision} including the total generated insulin amount, the amounts
127     * for the individual {@link BolusCalcComponent}s, and the conditions which resulted in this calculation.
128     */
129    public BolusCalcDecision parse(BolusCalcCondition ...ignoredConditions) {
130        if (userInputParameters.units != null) {
131            return new BolusCalcDecision(
132                    BolusCalcUnits.fromUser(userInputParameters.units),
133                    Set.of(new BolusCalcCondition.DataDecision("using user-provided insulin amount")));
134        }
135
136        Set<BolusCalcCondition> ignored = Arrays.stream(ignoredConditions).collect(Collectors.toSet());
137
138        Set<BolusCalcCondition> conditions = new TreeSet<>();
139
140        BolusCalcComponent addedFromCarbs = getAddedFromCarbs();
141        BolusCalcComponent addedFromBG = getAddedFromGlucose();
142        BolusCalcComponent addedFromIOB = getAddedFromIOB();
143
144
145        L.d(TAG, "addedFromCarbs: " + addedFromCarbs);
146        L.d(TAG, "addedFromBG: " + addedFromBG);
147        L.d(TAG, "addedFromIOB: " + addedFromIOB);
148
149        double total = addedFromCarbs.getUnits();
150
151        // above or at target
152        if (addedFromBG.getUnits() >= 0) {
153            // iob is higher than correction, so don't add either (carbs + max(0, bg + iob))
154            if (addedFromBG.getUnits() + addedFromIOB.getUnits() < 0) {
155                conditions.add(BolusCalcCondition.NO_POSITIVE_BG_CORRECTION);
156            } else if (addedFromBG.getUnits() + addedFromIOB.getUnits() == 0) {
157                // do nothing
158            } else {
159                // correction + iob adds a positive delta to the insulin
160                if (shouldApply(ignored, conditions, BolusCalcCondition.POSITIVE_BG_CORRECTION)) {
161                    total += addedFromBG.getUnits() + addedFromIOB.getUnits();
162                }
163            }
164        } else { // below target
165            if (addedFromBG.getUnits() + addedFromIOB.getUnits() == 0) {
166                // do nothing
167            } else if (total + addedFromBG.getUnits() + addedFromIOB.getUnits() > 0) { // correction + iob is less than the carb amount
168                if (shouldApply(ignored, conditions, BolusCalcCondition.NEGATIVE_BG_CORRECTION)) {
169                    total += addedFromBG.getUnits() + addedFromIOB.getUnits();
170                }
171            } else { // correction + iob takes the insulin amount negative
172                if (addedFromCarbs.getUnits() == 0) {
173                    // zero carbs, so don't apply condition
174                    total = 0.0;
175                } else if (shouldApply(ignored, conditions, BolusCalcCondition.SET_ZERO_INSULIN)) {
176                    total = 0.0;
177                }
178            }
179        }
180
181        conditions.addAll(addedFromCarbs.getConditions());
182        conditions.addAll(addedFromBG.getConditions());
183        conditions.addAll(addedFromIOB.getConditions());
184
185        BolusCalcUnits bolusCalcUnits = new BolusCalcUnits(total, addedFromCarbs.getUnits(), addedFromBG.getUnits(), addedFromIOB.getUnits(), 0);
186
187        L.d(TAG, "bolusCalculator: " + bolusCalcUnits + ", " + conditions);
188        Validate.isTrue(bolusCalcUnits.getTotal() >= 0);
189
190        // If there are any FailedPreconditions, then return 0 units regardless
191        for (BolusCalcCondition condition : conditions) {
192            if (condition instanceof BolusCalcCondition.FailedSanityCheck) {
193                return new BolusCalcDecision(BolusCalcUnits.fromUser(0), conditions);
194            }
195        }
196
197        return new BolusCalcDecision(bolusCalcUnits, conditions);
198    }
199
200    private boolean shouldApply(Set<BolusCalcCondition> ignored, Set<BolusCalcCondition> conditions, BolusCalcCondition condition) {
201        if (ignored.contains(condition)) {
202            conditions.add(new BolusCalcCondition.IgnoredDecision(condition));
203            return false;
204        } else {
205            conditions.add(condition);
206            return true;
207        }
208    }
209
210    /**
211     * @return the {@link BolusCalcUnits} representing the total estimated amount of insulin and the
212     * components which resulted in this estimation
213     */
214    public BolusCalcUnits getUnits() {
215        return parse().getUnits();
216    }
217
218    /**
219     * @return a set of {@link BolusCalcCondition}s which contain human-readable descriptions of
220     * how and why this estimate was made
221     */
222    public Set<BolusCalcCondition> getConditions() {
223        return parse().getConditions();
224    }
225
226    /**
227     * @return true if the user inputted a manual insulin amount, and that is being used instead of
228     * the suggested amount from the bolus calculation
229     */
230    public boolean isOverriddenByUser() {
231        return userInputParameters.units != null;
232    }
233
234    private static BolusCalcComponent zeroWithCondition(BolusCalcCondition one, BolusCalcCondition... more) {
235        List<BolusCalcCondition> list = new ArrayList<>();
236        list.add(one);
237        list.addAll(Arrays.asList(more));
238
239        return new BolusCalcComponent(0.0, list);
240    }
241}
